Package: SfSpHelpers
Type: Package
Title: Some functions to deal with sf/sp objects
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Charles Gauvin
Maintainer: Charles Gauvin <charles.gauvin1232@gmail.com>
Description: Basic utility functions such as adding centroids without changing the geometry, download geojsons and zipped shp files, 
    ensuring polygons are valid, compatibility with leaflet (geometries have no name, z and m coordinates are removed, etc)
License: MIT LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
